INFORMATION

In planning your trip or tour, secure a road map from your local service station for the trip that you expect to take. Plan your trip from this map, noting the route and cities that you are to pass through, then you can make note of the accommodations in the cities that you are to pass through in case you might want to stop over. No maps are published in our guide as they would not be legible for your convenience.

DON’T BE DISAPPOINTED—Make reservations in ad-
